OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775761868
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth II's Olympics stunt
OL,4,Cdouble outfit featured in fashion
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FQueen Elizabeth II's stunt double's
OL,8,Fdress, complete with bloomers, will be
OL,9,Fpart of an exhibition showcasing the
OL,10,Flate monarch's wardrobe.
OL,12,FHer trademark headscarves, see-through
OL,13,FFulton umbrellas, tweed suits and
OL,14,Flavish dresses worn at state occasions
OL,15,Fare featured in the event, which has
OL,16,Fsold out its first few weeks with
OL,17,Fthousands of tickets snapped up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
