PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775761868
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth II's Olympics stunt
OL,4,Cdouble outfit featured in fashion
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FThe Queen famously took part in the
OL,8,FLondon 2012 Olympics opening ceremony,
OL,9,Fappearing to millions to skydive into
OL,10,Fthe Olympic Stadium from a helicopter
OL,11,Fwith James Bond actor Daniel Craig,
OL,12,Fafter he escorted her from Buckingham
OL,13,FPalace.
OL,15,FHer stunt double leapt above the arena
OL,16,Fin a dress with sown-in Victorian-
OL,17,Fstyle bloomers and a large zip at the
OL,18,Fback to accommodate his parachute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
