PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775761868
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth II's Olympics stunt
OL,4,Cdouble outfit featured in fashion
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FTwo identical dresses, designed by
OL,8,FAngela Kelly, are on display for the
OL,9,Ffirst time alongside a host of items
OL,10,Ffrom the Queen's wardrobe which was
OL,11,Fkept in her apartments before her
OL,12,Fdeath in September 2022 and are now
OL,13,Funder the care of the Royal Collection.
OL,15,FExhibition curator Caroline de Guitaut
OL,16,Fsaid: "I think she had a definite
OL,17,Fsense of what suited her. She
OL,18,Fabsolutely knew how she wanted to
OL,19,Fappear."
OL,26,@xD@GOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
