OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775761868
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth II's Olympics stunt
OL,4,Cdouble outfit featured in fashion
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FOpening on Friday at the King's
OL,8,FGallery at Buckingham Palace, Queen
OL,9,FElizabeth II: Her Life in Style will
OL,10,Fbring together around 300 garments and
OL,11,Fitems from the Queen's wardrobe for
OL,12,Fthe largest exhibition staged of her
OL,13,Fclothing.
OL,15,FSpanning 10 decades, the show charts
OL,16,Fher evolution from young princess to
OL,17,FBritain's longest-reigning monarch,
OL,18,Fexploring how fashion became one of
OL,19,Fher most powerful tools of
OL,20,Fcommunication.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
