PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775761868
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth II's Olympics stunt
OL,4,Cdouble outfit featured in fashion
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FColour was important element of the
OL,8,Fmonarchy's soft power and the Queen
OL,9,Fused it to complement hosts, like the
OL,10,Fexhibition's Norman Hartnell gown in
OL,11,Fgreen and white, Pakistan's national
OL,12,Fcolours, worn at a banquet during a
OL,13,F1961 state visit to the Commonwealth
OL,14,Fnation.
OL,16,FShe opted for bright or distinctive
OL,17,Fshades at large events like away-days
OL,18,Faround the country or garden parties
OL,19,Fso she could be easily spotted by
OL,20,Fguests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
