PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775761868
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth II's Olympics stunt
OL,4,Cdouble outfit featured in fashion
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FThe Queen adapted her style to suit
OL,8,Fthe period and, speaking about her
OL,9,Flong list of designers, the curator
OL,10,Fsaid: "Of course, they would insert
OL,11,Fwhatever the contemporary prevailing
OL,12,Ffashion of the time. The hemline `
OL,13,FHardy Amies said 'we went as high as
OL,14,Fwe dared' in the 60s'.
OL,16,F"But at the end of the day, it's down
OL,17,Fto practicality, It's down to what
OL,18,Fenables her to carry out her duties, I
OL,19,Fthink, that was always there, that was
OL,20,Falways present.
OL,26,@rD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
