PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775761868
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth II's Olympics stunt
OL,4,Cdouble outfit featured in fashion
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,F"But that's not to say that she
OL,8,Fdoesn't have this important
OL,9,Fcontribution and interest `
OL,10,Fcontribution to British fashion, and
OL,11,Finterest in fashion, which is
OL,12,Fsomething that has always been sort of
OL,13,Fput on the sidelines."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
