PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775761868
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth II's Olympics stunt
OL,4,Cdouble outfit featured in fashion
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FClothes worn at milestone moments
OL,8,Fduring the Queen's 96-year life are
OL,9,Falso on display, from the historic
OL,10,Fchristening robe commissioned by Queen
OL,11,FVictoria for the baptism of future
OL,12,FEdward VII to a wedding dress created
OL,13,Fby Sir Norman Hartnell and the late
OL,14,Fmonarch's coronation dress.
OL,16,FQueen Elizabeth II: Her Life in Style
OL,17,Fis at the King's Gallery, Buckingham
OL,18,FPalace, will run from April 10 to
OL,19,FOctober 18.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
